title: Trend Of July 1/22: Hank Aaron, DJT, Marco Rubio, Dave Chappelle, Jane Krakowski
itunes:title: Trend Of July 1/22: Hank Aaron, DJT, Marco Rubio, Dave Chappelle, Jane Krakowski
description:
On this edition of Trend Of July Jack and Miles discuss the passing of Baseball legend Hank Aaron, "Donald John Trump" is trending after Chuck Schumer accidentally said "erection" on the Senate floor, Marco Rubio and other Republicans are threatening to bring impeachment proceedings against Biden, Dave Chappelle has tested positive for COVID-19, and Jane Krakowski was once in a 9-month relationship with the MyPillow guy!
